de-description =
    The official German (de) language pack for the FreeSynergy platform.

    Provides complete German translations for the desktop shell, all built-in apps
    (Node, Store, Browser, Lenses, Managers), help texts, and Store package descriptions.
    Maintained by the FreeSynergy team with 100% coverage.

de-features =
    - Full German translations for all FreeSynergy programs
    - Store package names, summaries, and descriptions
    - Help texts and field labels in German
    - Mozilla Fluent (.ftl) format — easy to contribute
    - Maintained by the FreeSynergy team
